item.title: I need help running moparscape please help i realy want to play?
item.dc:creator: @Zzz_O_zzZ Zzz O zzZ
item.description:
@Zzz_O_zzZ wrote:

All you need is moparscape to go on servers that have a no-ip.

Load Moparscape 3.2, click new server and enter the i.p. it tells you to enter. You also might need to change port but they are usually always 43594.

For ham servers you have to google search, download hamachi, and when it loads turn power on at bottom left hand side, and click the little triangle and name and pass will come up, on advertisement threads it will show you what you need to put in ex. pkkings3 pass 123.
Also with ham you have to change the server to what it tells you to change to.
